.TH story-slicer 1 "01/12/2023" "0.1.0"
.SH NAME
story-slicer \- A command-line tool to slice videos for social-media stories 
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B story-slicer
\fIinput-file\fR
\fIoutput-dir\fR
[\fImax-length\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B story-slicer
splits a given video file into multiple video files of an optionally specified fixed length.
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
.BR input-file
The input video file.
.TP
.BR output-dir
The output directory where the slices have to be placed.
.TP
.BR max-length
Maximum length of individual slices.
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
